extends layout.pug

block content

  article.portfolio-intro


    h1 My Portfolio
 
    p Below you can find the projects I worked on. Many of them are focused on enhancing user experience, such as project on data pagination or interactive form. Others are more concerned with certain tasks, like OOP in "Phrase Hunter" game or working with public API requests in project 5. I used JavaScript, HTML, CSS, Node and Express. For more details and technologies used, please click on the project.


  article.portfolio-project-thumbs
    .projects-box.box.grid
      each project in projects 
        .cell
          a(href=`/project/${project.id}`)
            img.thumbnail(src=`${project.image_urls[0]}`, alt=`${project.alt}`)
            h5= `${project.project_name}`

